tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played in 4 PGA TOUR Canada events as an amateur, all in Winnipeg (2008 and 2009 Players Cup, 2005 and 2006 MTS Classic)
tourBios.otherInfo: Had three Top-10 finishes during senior year at Boise State (2009/2010), 4- time Manitoba Willington Cup team member
tourBios.prYrSeason: Re-gained non-exempt status with rounds of 72-77-73-74 at the 2012 Fall Qualifying School, Earned exempt status with rounds of 74-73-72-76 at the 2012 California Qualifying School.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was 58th in 2011 at the Dakota Dunes Open.
